overview.en: Rating Token tokens are currently issued and operated only by the Singapore Foundation. They are inseparable and do not support transactions. As a consensus tool of the whole community and platform, token promotes community building, encourages more ratings experts to join the de-centralized rating platform, and finds high-quality block chain projects.
overview.zh: RatingToken令牌目前仅由新加坡基金会发放和运营，不可分割。令牌作为整个社区和平台的共识工具，促进社区的共建，激励更多的评级专家加入去中心化评级平台，发现优质的区块链项目。
